1586
02:34:24.865 --> 02:34:26.591
Dharma sir has changed so much!

1587
02:34:26.615 --> 02:34:27.740
Charlie!

1588
02:34:27.781 --> 02:34:29.156
Karuppa, you're in love, huh?

1589
